org.apache.ignite.streamer.window

Class StreamerBoundedSizeSortedWindow<E>

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.ignite.streamer.window.StreamerWindowAdapter<E>
      • org.apache.ignite.streamer.window.StreamerBoundedSizeSortedWindow<E>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Iterable<E>, LifecycleAware, StreamerWindow<E>, StreamerWindowMBean

    public class StreamerBoundedSizeSortedWindow<E>
extends StreamerWindowAdapter<E>
    Size-bounded sorted window. Unlike StreamerBoundedSizeWindow, which limits window only on size, this window also provides events in sorted order.
